OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FQuit your Ofsted roles,    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FPerry's sister tells heads 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Head teachers in England should stop   
OL,6, serving as Ofsted inspectors, says the 
OL,7, sister of a head who took her own life 
OL,8, after an inspection.                   
OL,10,FRuth Perry died while waiting for a    
OL,11,Freport that downgraded her school.     
OL,13,FProf Julia Waters was speaking to      
OL,14,Fmembers of a head teachers' union which
OL,15,Fis also asking members who work as     
OL,16,FOfsted inspectors to consider quitting.
OL,18,FOfsted said most school leaders thought
OL,19,Finspections were "constructive and     
OL,20,Fcollaborative".                        
